title: Post one-rep maxes here
body:
No boasting or exaggerating, please. I want to have a feel of where I am compared to other gamers. I started lifting some time in August (September?) and I've improved quite a bit. Most of my dumbbell lifts have gone from 15lb to 35, and I can actually use plates (45s) on my bar lifts.

Squat: ~150
Bench: ~135-140


I don't do much else other than various auxiliaries. Should probably add dead lifts and cleans.
